
=  Networganizing multi-lingual whistle-blowing activity and labour action that primarily targets TNC networks


=Description=

"Work groups will initially scan and analyse the leaked documents that are released by Wikileaks, like the Global Intelligence Files as well as other groups like Anonymous, GlobalLeaks. What will we be looking for in such meta-data will be about violations aginst producer, designer, users and consumer rights; such as stolen data, planned obsoloscence, illegal and dangerous material use, caputure and misuse of user-costumer data including selling the data to companies, production related threats to workers and public health.

Further more we will networganise multi-lingual whistle-blowing activities, primarily targeting largest TNC networks. 

We will turn the information into secure campaign intelligence, either to use in global actions we will launch as GNUnion, or feed-in and support ongoing union actions. In cases where there is an already organised independant union active, weather in the main company or its subsidairity, we will support their actions by desiging and forging global online viral campaigns."
